---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials — What Our Partners Say" description="Hear from the teams we've delivered for. Real feedback from long-term partnerships.">

  <div class="testimonials-page">
    <div class="wide-wrap">
      <h1>What our partners say</h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Real feedback from the teams we deliver for.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <img src="/images/logos/breeze.svg" alt="Breeze" class="testimonial-card-logo" />
        <blockquote>"They can build anything and do so beautifully and on time. They have also helped me tremendously in thinking strategically, even if it means I'm paying them less in the short term."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-card-author">
          <img src="/images/team/josh-turnbull.png" alt="Dr. Josh Turnbull" class="testimonial-card-avatar" />
          <div>
            <span class="testimonial-card-name">Dr. Josh Turnbull</span>
            <span class="testimonial-card-role">CEO, Breeze Oral Care</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <img src="/images/logos/odie.png" alt="Odie" class="testimonial-card-logo" />
        <blockquote>"Nolte has been our technology partner for three years. They've never missed a regulatory deadline, and the delivery model means we always know exactly what we're getting and what it costs."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-card-author">
          <div class="testimonial-card-initials">MB</div>
          <div>
            <span class="testimonial-card-name">Mo Bharucha</span>
            <span class="testimonial-card-role">CEO, Odie</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <img src="/images/logos/pilou.png" alt="Pilou" class="testimonial-card-logo" />
        <blockquote>"What stood out was the transparency. Every delivery had a price before we approved it, every timeline was visible in real time, and there were zero surprises on any invoice."</blockquote>
        <div class="testimonial-card-author">
          <div class="testimonial-card-initials">LD</div>
          <div>
            <span class="testimonial-card-name">Laurent Dupont</span>
            <span class="testimonial-card-role">CEO, Pilou</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</Base>

<style>
  .testimonials-page {
    padding: 8rem 2rem 5rem;
  }
  .testimonials-page h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .testimonials-grid {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 3rem auto 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }
  .testimonial-card-logo {
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
    filter: brightness(0);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .testimonial-card blockquote {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .testimonial-card-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .testimonial-card-avatar {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .testimonial-card-initials {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .testimonial-card-name {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
  }
  .testimonial-card-role {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonial-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
